data.description: This gorgeous 4 bedroom MOVE-IN READY house has been recently updated. Updates to include NEW WINDOWS that provide lots of natural light, NEW ROOF, NEW HVAC, updated ELECTRICAL and PLUMBING. From the open concept to the large shaded backyard, there is plenty of room for the whole family to enjoy. Recent updates include NEW LVP FLOORING, CARPET and STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES. You'll find tasteful upgrades that make this home shine! Like it's beautiful white SHAKER CABINETS with SOFT CLOSE DOORS and GRANITE COUNTER TOPS with a beautiful MATCHING ISLAND. The SHED is brand new and was custom built to store lawn items or even extra items to keep the home clutter free. The home is situated in a family friendly neighborhood and is conveniently located minutes from interstates, the naval shipyard and the newest attraction, RIVERS CASINO. Put this one FIRST on your list. This home will go FAST!
